title: IRIX.6.5.29-Overlays.1of3.iso
description:
This is the first CD you will need to update whatever version of IRIX 6.5 to 6.5.29. There are three CD images:

IRIX.6.5.29-Overlays.1of3.iso
IRIX.6.5.29-Overlays.2of3.iso
IRIX.6.5.29-Overlays.3of3.iso

You will need all of these to do an upgrade. If you want to do a fresh install you will also need the two Foundation CD&#039;s for IRIX 6.5. Along with this set of CD&#039;s you can optionally (recommended) get:

Applications.Feb.2006.iso
Complementary.Applications.Feb.2006.iso
